{"tid":497181,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"用左一個月時間終於睇曬全集clone wars","createTime":"2017-12-12T13:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T09:36:04.000Z","uid":59328,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"011760c45940870f27eba27cc962276c19fe2535","tid":497181,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T13:10:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/205413_e4998b29d9963026c398f4f391c6fcc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F205413_e4998b29d9963026c398f4f391c6fcc5.jpg&h=d7701573&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為要開台玩Lego Clone Wars，所以特登一口氣將全部120幾集clone wars煲鬼曬去(雙失廢青好多時間)。本來睇頭個幾季clone wars好鬼死歡樂，大家嘻嘻哈哈衝去唔同星球打仗，班Jedi同白兵個個做曬正義使者，拯救萬民於水深火熱之中。成個套路根本就係正義聯盟超人打怪獸。不過隨著集數愈來愈後，劇情就愈來愈黑，首都Coruscant先後多次發生恐襲以致議長不惜令共和國破產都要盲目增兵；到後來第五季Barriss黑化炸掉Jedi神殿使Ahsoka被冤枉而離開Jedi議會；最後一季仲出現埋有複制人有bug屎提前執行Order 66，搞到議長要親手殺人滅口隱藏陰謀。難怪迪迪尼無再拍Clone Wars下去，因為Clone Wars已黑過杯墨水，再拍落去肯定嚇親班米老鼠小朋友。"},{"pid":"85dca75d9681b6c9f5459ec3da10030eb68e7fea","tid":497181,"uid":55233,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T13:31:57.000Z","msg":"當年就係因為佢先認識star wars入坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可惜俾人腰斬咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0a00ac19f66becc6aeada7a4e68902b4b85a33","tid":497181,"uid":22876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T13:56:02.000Z","msg":"畫質超班 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906f731e0ba2a6ca31b9a927d5b04d840af8a2e4","tid":497181,"uid":33734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:41:46.000Z","msg":"呢套真係神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" cla